name: The juggler of life
description:
It's not a simple thing even though he makes it seem that way. To walk among bicycles and sneakers with three allied sticks in a world where avenues and buildings and suits and zeros dominate. Sometimes life is a battle and sometimes it's stopping to look at the roses. One way or another he always throws the sticks up and catches them with his three eyes or drops them with his six hands. Each shot brings him his next destination. Sometimes he has fun, sometimes he gets tired, sometimes he lives. 

Necochea, Argentina.
